name: You do not have a name
name_original: You do not have a name
description:
You do not have a name. You do not need one.

You do not have a name is a visual novel about a person walking home.

Controls are simple, and it also has controller support. All you do is press enter, LMB, or the A button.

French translation is still under development. 

Made to practice with renpy. 

Follow my Twitter for any future updates.
